# Tombstone: HeroUI was removed 2026-07 (PR #29) along with this dir's sync
# script, but a stale .heroui-tw/ from an old checkout would be scanned by
# Tailwind's Oxide auto-detection (no tailwind.config.ts anymore) and silently
# re-add ~25 KB of dead HeroUI utilities to the built CSS. Keep it ignored;
# delete the directory if you still have one.
/.heroui-tw/

